{"type": "article", "id": 50218, "title": "不喜欢洗碗？可能你缺一套好用又好看的工具｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-12T23:27:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47785, "name": "objéo"}, {"id": 47786, "name": "Hugo Tejada"}, {"id": 47787, "name": "Compartes"}, {"id": 47788, "name": "Nikita Melnikov"}, {"id": 47789, "name": "Achille & Pier Giacomo Castiglioni"}, {"id": 47790, "name": "Färg & Blanche"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 159, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180212211804Xf96ol4An0DILzhx.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Norma Sofa by Färg &amp; Blanche</h3><p>这款名为 Norma 的沙发最先亮相于斯德哥尔摩家具展，设计方是瑞典设计二人组 Färg &amp; Blanche。不同色彩和面料的组合，能够给予沙发多样化的外观。沙发与扶手椅系列利用分层原则将由不同面料拼接而成的三个部分组合在一起。</p><p>Norma 的灵感来源于随意扔在沙发上的毯子，或是用一种、两种、三种差异化的材质或色彩，最终组合出的产品效果将完全不同。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122118361LjkRF6MSq5lOApN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702934\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211836sn97WINtvSVP2TeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.649144\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122118370bLwqMZiVgtS21yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211838yXBx1F9KSLjU26dD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211842W8cJhdvAoFOyHk03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211843bsruS8wBeyE4Kg3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Heart Signature Truffles by Compartes</h3><p>情人节送巧克力很俗套？但每年情人节，巧克力作为礼物都是热门选择，只要有精致的美味和足够的创意。洛杉矶手工巧克力品牌 Compartes 有很多为人所喜爱的理由，包括 donuts &amp; coffee, biscuits &amp; honey, popcorn, s’mores, waffle cone 以及 cereal bowl 等超多口味帮它掳获了大批粉丝，引人注目的包装更是令其在巧克力界别具风格。</p><p>比如这个特别适合在情人节档期推出的心形巧克力礼盒，棱角分明的几何结构礼盒表面，细密线条中暗藏单词 LOVE，或是恋人拥吻的画面，适合含蓄、高级地表达爱意，它刻意避开了情人节礼品惯用的粉红色系或是金色系，揭开礼盒，里面则是 35 颗图案丰富多擦的巧克力。售价 99.95 美元，<a href=\"https://compartes.com/products/valentines-heart-chocolate-box\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211911vg96uOabqQ1kH0GM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122119141eZKHVkntuirjWX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211918OGYC9VHs1icSIlRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212211922qQfbaOp0u7ciHTrC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TAKE A WAY: A Portable Lamp by Hugo Tejada</h3><p>KAISHI 是一家总部位于西班牙的照明公司，刚刚推出了一种名为 TAKE A WAY 的便携式灯具。设计师 Hugo Tejada 受到旧火车站老式灯笼的启发，决定重新设计一个更具当代质感的灯笼，保持其新鲜感。</p><p>这款便携式灯具可以在任何需要额外照明的地方使用，因其内置超长寿命锂电池，可不受电线的限制。灯是由铝制成的，保证其耐用性和轻便性。此外，它配备了可调节 LED 技术，可以根据需要控制亮度。白色的铝制外部饰有金色或木质手柄，增加了观赏性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122124495bvksT3yn0g1KSmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.967187\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212450uF83WSvY6RkET7DX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212450jWhR7BqVyN9EiMIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212450Ee7JBdLRSQcFfOMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.267969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212450cbJHa5RTS3jw8e0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212451PQclp9jyGwHMmxqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dishwashing Toolset by objéo</h3><p>对于很多人来说，洗碗是一件可怕的事情，最重要的是，大多数洗碗工具和海绵都欠缺设计感，或者说设计得功能不当。</p><p>总部位于蒙特利尔的小型家居产品公司 objéo，推出了一套木制洗碗工具，包括洗碗刷、海绵和洗涤器等，每一个工具都可以放在木架上，不用时可以晾置干燥。售价 30 至 35 美元，<a href=\"https://www.objeo.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212051XhMa5rwtpxszQ9mP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212051MbKLBxi0yHYXd3D9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212052idEInzpok5WG30XT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212052EpRzIVMKq587wDXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212059scvQqFVTIGEh2wjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Snoopy 50th Limited Edition by Achille &amp; Pier Giacomo Castiglioni</h3><p>为了纪念大师 Achille Castiglioni 的杰出设计，经过他女儿的授权，意大利灯具品牌 Flos 推出了其在 1967 年设计的台灯 Snoopy 的限量版，纪念其面世 50 周年。全球发行 1701 个，新版为 LED 版本（原版是卤素灯）。Castiglioni 的原版为 Magis 创作。新版灯罩采用 1967 年样品时的黑色磨砂版，限量版全球统一带编号证书，欧洲和中国同步发行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212135heEATbln6u9IP2M8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.101695\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212136XQciFN9OVhokWlpM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212137EkLxf5U2FcyPKrIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.101695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212138aVzR8HAS17IxcshW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GIF by Nikita Melnikov</h3><p>GIF 动画虽然仅有几秒的展现时间，却能展示出丰富的情感和故事内涵。不仅是看着好玩，还能拿来做表情包。来自白俄罗斯的平面设计师 Nikita Melnikov 做的这一组 GIF 图，萌趣十足。不管是冰淇淋、披萨、行李箱还是 T 恤、说“不”的小猫、城堡、小狗等等，可爱的形象、情绪都很丰富饱满。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021221272498VonEZeFPQLqsiC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212640tYpqiTcH1sfOXykS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122122239dBIO53SZeXHviPq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212245MonqyKwBYU49D381.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802122122463jeqUDxskdbvTYCM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212246vumO1SdUwhe7qTMJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212212255IxUGsCkEAyX68vmY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}